= Super Mario Odyssey =
Super Mario Odyssey is a platform game developed and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo Switch . Released in 2017 , it is the 27th main installment in the Super Mario series . The game follows Mario as he travels across various kingdoms to rescue Princess Peach from Bowser , who plans to marry her . Super Mario Odyssey features open - world exploration , as well as new mechanics such as Mario 's ability to possess objects and enemies using his hat , Cappy .

The game received critical acclaim , with reviewers praising its creativity , level design , and soundtrack . It won several awards , including Best Platformer at the 2017 Game Critics Awards , and has sold over 25 million copies worldwide .

= Red Dead Redemption 2 =
Red Dead Redemption 2 is an action - adventure game developed and published by Rockstar Games for the PlayStation 4 , Xbox One , and Microsoft Windows . Released in 2018 , it is a prequel to the 2010 game Red Dead Redemption . The game follows Arthur Morgan , a member of the Van der Linde gang , as he navigates the American Old West in the early 1900s .

Red Dead Redemption 2 features an open world with dynamic weather and day - night cycles , as well as a complex story with themes of loyalty , morality , and the decline of the Wild West . The game received universal acclaim from critics , who praised its graphics , gameplay , and narrative . It has sold over 45 million copies worldwide .